description: Donald Trump, Ben Carson, Carly Fiorina, Sen. Marco Rubio, Gov. Jeb Bush, Sen. Rand Paul, Gov. Chris Christie, Gov. John Kasich, Sen. Ted Cruz, Gov. Mike Huckabee and Gov. Scott Walker square off in the 8 p.m. ET Republican presidential debate hosted by CNN.
title: Trump: ' Rand Paul should not be on this stage'
